               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 7ra-101rb)&#xD; I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns (fols. 7ra-11rb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 11rb-12rb)&#xD; I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki ... "I worship Thee ..." and other hymns (fols. 12rb-13vb)&#xD;
                     I-4) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 115 miracles (fols.
                     13va-101rb).</summary>
